WWW-Honeypot-httpBL version 0.01
=======================

A perl interface to Project Honeypot's http:BL service.

See http://www.projecthoneypot.org/ for more detail on the project and the blacklisting service (http:BL) they offer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Carp;
Net::hostent;
Socket;

